Word Lookup
Privacy Policy
Your Privacy
Your privacy is critically important to us. Your data is yours. No Personally-Identifying Information is collected or transmitted to external locations when using Word Lookup.
Information we do collect
Word Lookup collects aggregate, anonymous statistics, such as device type, operating system version, and percentage of users who use particular features, to help improve the app.
Your Consent
By using our site or apps, you consent to our privacy policy.
Contacting the Developer
If you have questions regarding this privacy policy, you may email the developer at feedback@appspired.com.
Changes to this policy
Any changes to this policy will be posted on this page.
